# DaisyUI Themes

The portal enables **all 35 built-in DaisyUI themes** via `themes: all` in [`src/routes/layout.css`](src/routes/layout.css).

Theme names live in [`src/lib/constants/daisyui-themes.ts`](src/lib/constants/daisyui-themes.ts).

| Special | Behavior |
|---------|----------|
| `system` | Follows OS light/dark → `winter` / `night` |
| Other names | Set `data-theme` on `<html>` (e.g. `cupcake`, `dracula`) |

Admins configure **allowed themes** and **default theme** in Settings → **Theme**.

Users pick from allowed themes in Settings or the navbar palette dropdown.

Do **not** hardcode only `winter`/`night` in new theme UI — use `APP_THEMES` / `getAllowedThemeOptions()`.

